<!--PageTitleFmt-->
        <div id='wikititle'>
          <div class='pagegroup'><a href='http://wiki.simplelog.net/Themes'>Themes</a> /</div>
          <h1 class='pagetitle'>Preferences</h1></div>
<!--PageText-->
<div id='wikitext'>
<p>Here are the preferences available for use in your theme. The values of these preferences are set in the preferences area of the admin section. You should also see available <a class='wikilink' href='Helpers'>helper methods</a> and <a class='wikilink' href='PostHelpers'>post helper methods</a>.
</p>
<p class='vspace'>You can return any preference listed below by using either <code>Site.<em>preference_name</em></code> or <code>get_pref('<em>preference_name</em>')</code> where <em>preference_name</em> is one of the following:
</p>
<div class='vspace'></div><hr />
<div class='vspace'></div><div class='prefs_list' >
<p><strong><code>archive_token</code></strong> How you wish to refer to your archives in <span class='wikiword'>URLs</span> (http://yoursite.com/<em>token</em>/1981/5/15/happy_birthday)
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>author_email</code></strong> Your email address.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>author_gender</code></strong> What is your gender? Useful for proper he/shes later.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>comment_subjects</code></strong> Allow commenter to add a subject line to comments? ('yes' or 'no')
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>commenting_on</code></strong> Turn the commenting features on? ('yes' or 'no')
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>copyright_year</code></strong> First year this site was under your copyright.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>custom_field_1</code></strong>  The name of custom field 1.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>custom_field_2</code></strong>  The name of custom field 2.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>custom_field_3</code></strong>  The name of custom field 3.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>date_format</code></strong> Date format used in views.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>delicious_username</code></strong> Your del.icio.us username, if you have one.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>domain</code></strong> Your site's domain, do not include http://
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>email_subject</code></strong> Contact emails sent through the default link will have this subject.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>encoding</code></strong> Site encoding.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>esbn</code></strong> Your ESBN, if you have one.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>extended_link_text</code></strong> Link text to use when entry has extended content.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>icbm</code></strong> Your <span class='wikiword'>GeoURL</span> ICBM address, if you have one.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>issn</code></strong> Your ISSN, if you have one.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>items_in_feed</code></strong> Number of posts to show in the RSS feed.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>items_on_index</code></strong> Number of posts to show on the index page.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>language</code></strong> Used in HTML DOCTYPE.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>mint_dir</code></strong> Mint location.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>rss_url</code></strong> Location of your RSS URL if not the default.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>search_results</code></strong> Number of items to return in quicksearch results.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>search_results_full</code></strong> Number of items to return in full search results.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>show_author_of_post</code></strong> Show the name of the author who wrote each post? ('yes' or 'no')
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>show_gravatars</code></strong> Include Gravatar icons in comment display? ('yes' or 'no')
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>site_description</code></strong> Used in the meta description tag.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>site_name</code></strong> Your site's name.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>site_primary_author</code></strong> Your name.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>slogan</code></strong> Your site's slogan, shown in the title of the index page.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>time_format</code></strong> Time format used in views.
</p>
<p class='vspace'><strong><code>warn_bad_browsers</code></strong> Want to warn users of bad browsers? ('yes' or 'no')
</p></div>
</div>

      </td>
    </tr></table>
